title: Puzzle 1 Decoded
author: Rasmase
pages:
#- so you want to hear a story eh? haha have i got a story for you! civcraft... this is our home but make no mistake - this is not a planet of peace and love, so now that i have your attention (totes original i might add) im sure you want to hear about
#- the treasure, you dont want to go to x:8481 y:24 z:6342. if i told you to go to x:4815 y:16 z:2342 you might be able to tell ive been watching lost, but those arent right. the treasure is at x:6082 y:128 z:3732 but only if you divide each value by two.
#- part two will be in the chest with a harder puzzle to a bigger treasure. bring that book to the carbon library before searching for the next treasure or i will! happy hunting!
